article.description: — Bryan Greenlee scored 14 points as Florida Atlantic romped past North Florida 76-41 on Sunday.
article.headline: Greenlee scores 14 to lift FAU past North Florida 76-41
article.linkText: Greenlee scores 14 to lift FAU past North Florida 76-41
article.story: BOCA RATON, Fla. -- — Bryan Greenlee scored 14 points as Florida Atlantic romped past North Florida 76-41 on Sunday. Michael Forrest had 13 points for the Owls (5-4). North Florida scored 12 points in the second half, its season low.
